# helpPreprocessor

- _helpPreprocessor(h)_

Run the help fragment pre-processor for the help topic _h_.
Read the file specified by the string _s_ .help.pre_ and apply the help pre-processor to generate the file _s.help.sl_.

~~~spl io
'On Integer Sequences'
.helpPreprocessor
~~~

* * *

See also: splHelpFragment

Guides: Help Functions
